	<h2>Activity and links</h2>
	<p>You can practise a lot of leisure activities like tennis, sailing, golf, you can have a boat trip in the bay, to Chausey and Jersey, a cruise on the river Rance to Dinan.</p>
    <p>It’ s also possible to cross the estuary by boat to Dinard (a lot of crossings every day).</p>
